37360>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37360>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37361>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37362>>>    End_Procedure
37363>>>    
37363>>>End_Object
